ordinalCont v1.2 (Release date: 2017-06-16)
==============

Changes:

* non-parametric functions now with mean zero
* new parameters in the ocm function (n.int.knots and order)
* plot.ocm can now plot individual graphs
* possibility of choosing smoothing parameters
* no density graph in plot.ocm

ordinalCont v1.2.2 (Release date: 2017-11-30)
==============

Changes:

* predict.ocm bug fixes
* extra parameters in plot.ocm

ordinalCont v2.0.2 (Release date: 2019)
==============

Changes:

* original ordering of data in predict.ocm() is now respected


ordinalCont v2.0.4 (Release date: 2020)
==============

Changes:

* minor changes, version linked to published JSS paper


ordinalCont v2.0.5 (Release date: 2021)
==============

Changes:

* Working on predict.ocm() when new datasets are included
* prediction on observed scale with 95% CIs